      {
        "Id": "f7f4c42aa9a24d48b9ad7a8b7b7800b2",
        "Title": "Excel Report generator",
        "DescriptionText": "ExcelGen + Config\nTakes the Param Writer's output and generates a formatted multi-sheet Excel report. Automatically adds a second \"All Updates Only\" sheet filtering to only rows where something actually changed — either a parameter was written or the connector was moved. Cells highlight yellow on a per-column basis: only the specific Original/Updated pairs that actually changed turn yellow, not the whole row. The Moved and Update Status columns highlight independently. Falls back to Desktop if the save path is invalid, saves a timestamped copy if the file is locked. Config supplies the save path (Update_Data_Report.xlsx), sheet names (Connector Updates, Metrics), and color theme (Blue).",
